Joseph Thompson (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseph_Thompson_(actor) 0 Joseph Thompson is a British theatre, screen and voice actor best known for playing the sociopath Dr. Paul Browning in the British Channel 4 serial drama Hollyoaks. He studied at the University of Bristol and trained as an actor at the Webber Douglas Academy of Dramatic Art.
